pe":"paragraph","text":"一、主要的右派言行：","index":124,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"45b0edf2a5","type":"appellation","text":"1、辱骂党团员“就象从前的特务一样”，“象贵族一样，享乐在前，吃苦在后”。侮蔑人民代表大会“都是一个调，只是举举手，不准发表不同的意见。”","index":125,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"c7d7d01881","type":"appellation","text":"2、说彭真同志动员反右派斗争的报告“头脑发热，小题大做”，诬蔑反右派斗争是“大胆假设，小心求证。”","index":126,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"bc2f542662","type":"paragraph","text":"二、斗争后的态度：","index":127,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"40cd13eebd","type":"paragraph","text":"承认错误，并揭发了同班右派分子的材料。","index":128,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"33c427e9bd","type":"paragraph","text":"三、处理意见：","index":129,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"bc4caa005b","type":"paragraph","text":"开除团籍，留校察看。","index":130,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"af32343d77","type":"subtitle","text":"四、免于行政处分的二人","index":131,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"9014a64f17","type":"subtitle","text":"1、张保正","index":132,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"a9c04e1f46","type":"paragraph","text":"团员，男，23岁，家庭出身工人，北京大学化学系三年级学生，一般右派分子。","index":133,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"fd87a75591","type":"paragraph","text":"一、主要的右派言行：","index":134,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"90278854ce","type":"subtitle","text":"污蔑政治分类名单是“黑名单”，煽动同学讨论“黑名单”问题，说团组织是“挂羊头卖狗肉”，自称是反对派。","index":135,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"a043a9c934","type":"paragraph","text":"二、斗争后的态度：","index":136,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"d6839d132d","type":"paragraph","text":"低头认罪，愿意痛改前非，积极参加了反右派斗争。","index":137,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"f6f07126a3","type":"paragraph","text":"三、处理意见：","index":138,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"04dd69aeee","type":"paragraph","text":"开除团籍，从宽处理，免于行政处分，留校学习。","index":139,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"3d76cd9877","type":"subtitle","text":"2、刘世偕","index":140,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"cbec0c11e4","type":"paragraph","text":"预备党员，男，23岁，家庭出身资本家，清华大学无线电系四年级学生，一般右派分子。","index":141,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"35d9b76fa0","type":"paragraph","text":"一、主要的右派言行：","index":142,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"405956dc95","type":"paragraph","text":"1、参与组织反动小集团“学生俱乐部”，企图夺取党对整风的领导。访问极右分子钱伟长，要钱来领导全校鸣放。","index":143,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"d0301a144e","type":"appellation","text":"2、支持右派言论，说“为了真理，不怕开除党籍”。","index":144,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"068d3155cd","type":"paragraph","text":"二、斗争后的态度：","index":145,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"0277c0dae5","type":"paragraph","text":"承认错误，作了检讨，交代“学生俱乐部”活动后，揭发别的右派分子，积极参加反右派斗争。","index":146,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"8d411527f0","type":"paragraph","text":"三、处理意见：","index":147,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"bd8472cc59","type":"paragraph","text":"开除党籍，从宽处理，免于行政处分，留校学习。","index":148,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"1b6ede91b5","type":"subtitle","text":"五、按反革命分子或按刑事犯罪分子逮捕法办的五人","index":149,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"f90c31ae65","type":"subtitle","text":"1、刘奇弟","index":150,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"41c4a95f82","type":"paragraph","text":"男，25岁，家庭出身职员，北京大学物理系四年级学生。","index":151,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"0ec7169e53","type":"paragraph","text":"一、反革命罪行：","index":152,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"84633521bf","type":"appellation","text":"1、在肃反运动时，曾喊“打倒共产党”的反动口号，并写了‘‘释放胡风”、“任命胡风为中华人民国副主席”、“处决一切共产党员”的反动传单，因而被捕，后被宽大释放。","index":153,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"56af363549","type":"appellation","text":"2、整风开始后，疯狂进攻肃反运动和为胡风“喊冤”，张贴“白毛女”、“胡风不是反革命”等反动大字报，写“铁窗禁贤良，天昏地也暗，忠臣血洒地，鬼神俱哭泣”等反动诗文多篇。在北大煽起了一股反对肃反运动的逆流。","index":154,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"ef2d8edf09","type":"appellation","text":"3、刘是反动小集团“百花学社”的发起人，反动刊物“广场”的编委，并与极右分子谭天荣等到天津的高等学校点火。","index":155,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"6e5daf1036","type":"paragraph","text":"斗争后仍顽抗抵赖，不肯低头认罪。l0月19日晚，扰乱批判右派分子的会场，并动手打了八个同学，并一人的手咬破。当夜，群众将他扭送公安局，已依法逮捕。","index":156,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"32e5cb6064","type":"subtitle","text":"2、陈奉孝","index":157,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"9e07945640","type":"paragraph","text":"男，21岁，家庭出身资本家。北京大学数学力学系三年级学生。","index":158,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"689ac3ffb9","type":"paragraph","text":"一、反革命罪行：","index":159,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"26627e465d","type":"appellation","text":"1、联合北大反革命分子顾文选、谭金水、贺泳增、赵清等组织秘密反革命小组织，积极进行反党、反人民政权的活动。力求扩大组织和寻求幕后支持者，曾数次在英国代办处、印度大使馆和南斯拉夫大使馆求见(受阻未成)，要求北大讲师极右分子黄继忠替他联系外籍教授温德(原美籍，有特务嫌疑)，请求资助。","index":160,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"c6453eb5ed","type":"appellation","text":"2、勾结极右分子谭天荣等政治反动小集团“百花学社”，并油印反动刊物“广场”五百余册，分发到各地高等学校。","index":161,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"73e01c6936","type":"appellation","text":"3、组织极右分子谭天荣、刘奇弟等人分赴本市八所高等学校和天津四个院校点火。","index":162,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"e8243784ef","type":"paragraph","text":"斗争后仍公开表示“宁可粉身碎骨，也不向保守派让半步”，决心顽抗到底。后到天津企图混进外国轮船逃往香港，被公安局逮捕。","index":163,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"8b961c5623","type":"subtitle","text":"3、孙宝琮","index":164,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"fa345de83a","type":"paragraph","text":"男，27岁，家庭出身资本家，清华大学电机系三年级学生。肃反时曾被斗。","index":165,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"bab651291c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、反革命罪行：","index":166,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"89f26b3c5f","type":"appellation","text":"1、整风运动以前，即在学校秘密组织反革命集团。这个集团的成员大都是对党有阶级仇恨的人，并密约“结成生死之交”。","index":167,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"c93b055e8f","type":"appellation","text":"2、在整风运动中，趁机组织“庶民社；，出版反动壁报“庶民报”。曾派人与人大极右分子林希翎、北大极右分子谭天荣联系，企图组织联合战线。","index":168,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"ae4d372de1","type":"appellation","text":"3、反右派斗争开始后，指示小集团成员“作假检讨，分散组织学生社团，以保存实力，占领据点”。鼓动小集团成员“抛弃个人的一切，和共产党苦斗几十年”。并自称“决心跟共产党干一辈子”，“只要头不断，就要干下去”。","index":169,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"3332f90831","type":"paragraph","text":"二、斗争后的态度：","index":170,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"4180a3bfec","type":"paragraph","text":"顽抗到底，拒不悔改。","index":171,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"265584cb75","type":"paragraph","text":"三、处理意见：","index":172,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"6f985a5fce","type":"paragraph","text":"逮捕法办。","index":173,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"2718d96c7e","type":"subtitle","text":"4、何铁声","index":174,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"d3820858d9","type":"paragraph","text":"男，24岁，家庭出身地主兼资本家，人大财政系三年级学生。他的父亲解放前贩运鸦片，土改和五反中被斗争，现被政府管制。","index":175,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"58515ee83c","type":"paragraph","text":"一、反革命罪行：","index":176,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"2c9d8a03d5","type":"appellation","text":"1、今年2月在教室写了三条反革命标语：“消灭共产党不平等的组织机构”、“反对共产党”、“消灭腐朽的共产党”。","index":177,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"6e6499e982","type":"appellation","text":"2、整风开始后，向党中央和民主人士写信，对党大肆诬蔑，叫嚣“天下乌鸦一般黑”，“我对共产党不满，我要什么，我要杀人，杀掉官僚走狗们……。”还张贴大字报，煽动罢课游行。","index":178,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"a29759a8f4","type":"paragraph","text":"二、斗争后的态度：","index":179,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"8364a42b1e","type":"paragraph","text":"承认错误，悔改表现不好。","index":180,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"2046d9e2a5","type":"paragraph","text":"三、处理意见：","index":181,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"e8f927b3f9","type":"paragraph","text":"涂写反革命标语的现行反革命分子，逮捕法办。","index":182,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"309ce030bc","type":"subtitle","text":"5、李燕生","index":183,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"65eb0a7ec1","type":"paragraph","text":"男，23岁，北京大学化学系二年级学生，他的父亲是反动军官，三反时被捕，病死在狱中。","index":184,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"b72bdb443a","type":"paragraph","text":"主要的罪行：","index":185,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"53275fd361","type":"appellation","text":"1、原是团员，因伪造历史，道德败坏，被开除团籍。后因偷盗，曾被判刑十个月。","index":186,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"5fdbcae881","type":"appellation","text":"2、在整风运动中，组织反动社团“匹克威克”社，先后写了二十多张大字报。参加反动小集团“广场”编委会，曾与北大其他极右分子到颐和园开秘密会议。亲自刻印了反动宣传品“民主接力棒”，散发到天津、上海、武汉等地。","index":187,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"0c538d05cd","type":"appellation","text":"3、反右派斗争后期，又偷窃同学箱子两个。","index":188,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"},{"id":"c47fcc4d35","type":"paragraph","text":"按刑事犯罪分子，已经逮捕。","index":189,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9"}],"page":{"id":"c60da3347f","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5c26bfa0d9","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}